        "subject": "=Task Overdue: Immediate Attention Required – {{$json.task_title}}",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.project_manager_firstname}} {{$json.project_manager_lastname}},</p>\n\n<p>The task <b>{{$json.task_title}}</b> has exceeded its planned due date and is currently overdue.</p>\n\n<p><b>Overdue Details</b><br>\n* Task Title: {{$json.task_title}}<br>\n* Due Date: {{$json.task_due_date}}<br>\n* Overdue By: {{$json.overdue_days}} days<br>\n* Current Status: {{$json.task_status}}</p>\n\n<p>Please update the task with completion details or provide a revised plan to avoid escalation.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\nPMO – Escalation Desk</p>",
        "options": {}
